  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*braket = <Psi|Psi>: plain bilinear pairing (no conjugation), matching this notebook's existing\n  non-Hermitian convention. normRatio divides by G21's diagonal entry for the SAME state (G21 is\n  Section C's already-verified Gram matrix over states21) — only valid for (λ1,λ2)=(2,1) since\n  G21/states21 are fixed globals for that representation, matching this plan's fixed test case.*)\nClearAll[braket, normRatio];\nbraket[λ1_, λ2_][M_, n_] := PsiLeft[λ1, λ2][M, n] . Psi[λ1, λ2][M, n];\nnormRatio[λ1_, λ2_][M_, n_] := Module[{i = First[FirstPosition[states21, {M, n}]]},\n  braket[λ1, λ2][M, n]/G21[[i, i]]];\n(*smoke test*)\n{braket[2, 1][1, 0], normRatio[2, 1][1, 0]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352966\" data-output-id=\"45\" data-out-n=\"305\" data-sub-idx=\"5\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"50\" data-sub-start=\"9\" data-sub-end=\"9\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[305]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrnhf0bh-xch769u\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezcuMzY2MDg0MDMwMTY0MzE3OTExODEwNzI3MjczLTAuOTY4MDQ2Mjk5Nzk0NDYxNDAwMjY1ODg3NDI2OFwsXG1hdGhybXtpfSwxLjAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwKzAuXHRpbWVzIDEwXnstMjF9XCxcbWF0aHJte2l9XHJpZ2h0XH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2141em;vertical-align:-0.35em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">{</span></span><span class=\"mord\">7.366084030164317911810727273</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.9680462997944614002658874268</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1.00000000000000000000</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">21</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
