  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*RESOLUTION of the Phase-2 obstruction (cell 71): the functional object is not the bare bracket\n  br1[f] but the 1-site FSoV DETERMINANT det1[f] = br1[f]/f(θ1) — the 1-site reduction of Section\n  C's det[λ1,λ2][f] (which divides by f at BOTH nodes θ1,θ2; only the θ1-node survives at 1 site).\n  This missing 1/f(θ1) normalization is exactly what caused the obstruction: it cancels the\n  (k κ1)^(θ1/h) fractional prefactor between br1[f] and f(θ1), leaving\n  det1[k^(u/h) Q1] = Σ_j w_j k^j Q1(θ1+jh)/Q1(θ1), a CLEAN degree-λ1 polynomial in k with leading\n  term exactly 1 (since w_0=1 by Nn1's construction).*)\nClearAll[det1, FLdet];\ndet1[λ1_][f_] := br1[λ1][f]/(f /. u -> θ1);\nFLdet[λ1_, λ2_][M_, n_][k_] := det1[λ1][k^(u/h) Q1[λ1, λ2][M, n][u]];\n(*smoke: FLdet[1,2][0,0][k] must be a degree-1 polynomial in k, constant term exactly 1, NO\n  fractional power of k (unlike the old FL).*)\nFLdet[1, 2][0, 0][k] // Simplify",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352966\" data-output-id=\"64\" data-out-n=\"389\" data-sub-idx=\"5\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"71\" data-sub-start=\"12\" data-sub-end=\"12\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[389]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrnigqe6-xis35d2\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnQoMS4wMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDAwMDArMC5cdGltZXMgMTBeey0yN31cLFxtYXRocm17aX1ccmlnaHQpLVxsZWZ0KDAuMzYwNDM5ODc1MTQ3MjI2NTM3MjY2Njc3NjUxKzAuOTMyNzgyNDQ4NTkzMzc0NzE2NDg0ODM1OTgyXCxcbWF0aHJte2l9XHJpZ2h0KVwsaw==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2141em;vertical-align:-0.35em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\">1.000000000000000000000000000</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">27</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">)</span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">0.360439875147226537266677651</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.932782448593374716484835982</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[389]= \\left(1.000000000000000000000000000+0.\\times 10^{-27}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)-\\left(0.360439875147226537266677651+0.932782448593374716484835982\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,k",
